410
00:30:13.899 --> 00:30:15.596
He doesn't. he can't.

411
00:30:15.683 --> 00:30:17.772
- He mustn't.
- Where we left off. Santiago.

412
00:30:17.859 --> 00:30:20.166
Guido is hope. There
